==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: grouch
<hw>grouch</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to complain habitually, especially
about minor or routine annoyances.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> grumble, gripe.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>grouchy</ent>⟦br⟧
